{
  "texts": [
    "Whereas AI investments are expected to reach €22.4 billion (approximately $26.5 billion) in the European Union by 2025 (Alliance, 2020).",
    "On the contrary, developing countries struggle to secure funding.",
    "AI related initiatives are either minimal or completely absent in developing nations (Pro, 2018; Loucks et al., 2019).",
    "For instance, in African countries the process of securing loans for digitalization is quite cumbersome leading to its abandonment by the farmer or small agriculture firms (Aguera et al., 2020).",
    "It has been reported that a total of $140 million of seed-funding across the whole of Africa for AI startups was secured (Hamdan et al., 2021)."
  ]
}